div.div: Scoop the beans in the middle of the plate then add the bacon at 1-2 oclock, add the sausages at 3 oclock, then the eggs at 6. If you have blood pudding, pop that on at 8 oclock and then fill the rest of the plate with the tomatoes at 11 oclock and the mushrooms at 12. Fried bread can get tucked in wherever or placed on a side plate.
